	CREATE THE REAL WISP SHIP KIT
	=============================

	Create the real WISP SHIP KIT from the QA version.  Substitute the
	real version for "XXX" in the following commands.

	[ ]	Move and rename %WISP%\src\ship to %WISP%\shipXXX
		This needs to be done thru MS-WINDOWS as MS-DOS doesn't
		have commands to move or rename directories.


